Author: CallMeFrida
Text: Thank you for your comment! I tell myself that nothing is permanent, every day is new.

Author: Skiinky
Text: I love that you managed to finish with a positive outlook, and that attitude is exactly why you will beat this thing. In recovery the body is still settling and recovering and that's ok. It will get there eventually you just have to get through the hard parts first. You are doing amazingly, and I'm sure you are going to look stunning on the day. Try and remember that people don't see you the way you see yourself. Stay strong xx
